abstract: Security was beefed up Wednesday afternoon as the House managers prepared to march toward the Senate to deliver the articles of impeachment.
lead_paragraph: Golden stanchions with maroon velvet ropes were set up throughout the main hallway of the Capitol’s second floor as House managers prepared to march toward the Senate to deliver the articles of impeachment. Journalists — who are used to freely roaming the halls — will be required to stand behind the ropes as the formal procession passes by.
